{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>1.2 What are Tracing,snooping,Sampling,Profiling,and Observability</h2>\n<p>Tracing和Snooping指的是同一回事:收集事件,或者收集实践能力的容器.snoop只是早期的一个概念的指代.  </p>\n<p>Sampling: 采样,和Tracing类似 不过一般来讲指的是在一段时间内的对一堆事件的收集.  </p>\n<p>Observability:可观察性,指的我们对操作系统可以理解其运行状态的能力.  </p>\n<h2>1.3 What Are BCC,bpftrace,and IO Visor?</h2>\n<p>BCC:最早的tracing framework 底层用C,可以外接各种语言(python/lua/c++)\nbpftrace:新出的tracing framework的前端. 自己使用了一种语言.</p>\n<p>BCC和bpftrace都是前端,都依赖了相同的底层工具 libbcc/libbpf</p>\n<p>BCC和bpftrace都放在一个叫<a href=\"https://github.com/iovisor\">IO Visor</a>的项目中</p>\n<h2>1.4 A first Look at BCC: Quick Wins</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># install in ubuntu</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> bpfcc-tools linux-headers-<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">uname</span> -r<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>这种方法安装的bcc的工具会带有后缀<code class=\"language-text\">-bpfcc</code>所以实际执行的是</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> execsnoop-bpfcc  <span class=\"token comment\"># 展示进程创建</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> biolatency-bpfcc -m <span class=\"token comment\"># 展示IO读写时间</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2>1.8 A first Look at bpftrace: Tracing Open()</h2>\n<p>在ubuntu下使用<code class=\"language-text\">sudo apt install bpftrace -y</code>去安装bpftrace,不要装snap版的</p>","fields":{"slug":"/baseball/BPF Performance Tools/part1:technolgies/c1:Introduction/","disqus":{"shortname":"woodgear-blog"}},"frontmatter":{"id":"a61279","time":"2020-11-12T23:14:48+08:00","tag":null},"parent":{"__typename":"File","name":"c1:Introduction","ext":".md","birthTime":"1970-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","changeTime":"2020-11-26T15:05:48.118Z","relativeDirectory":"baseball/BPF Performance Tools/part1:technolgies","absolutePath":"/home/oaa/sm/ns/share/blog/baseball/BPF Performance Tools/part1:technolgies/c1:Introduction.md"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/baseball/BPF Performance Tools/part1:technolgies/c1:Introduction/","disqus":{"shortname":"woodgear-blog"}}}